                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18201206-197-off1154 t18201206-197-crimeloc1156"></join>. He remained there sixteen weeks, he said he had two guineas a-week from his brother. I never received a farthing from him - he left last Tuesday without notice. I found him at Hatton Garden two days after I missed this property, which was let with the lodgings.</p>
